	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conquereris de mea in scribendo raritate et negligentia; verum cum argumentum nullum sit dignum tuis studiis ac nostrę amicitię, satius duco tacere quam tibi negotiis aliis adobruto facessere negotium.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8073" cert="high">Gilbertus</persName> habet ad me missas literas, quas <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4575" cert="high">fratri</persName> suo perferendas dedi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName> consiliis tu melius nosti quam nos; molitur aliquid contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiam</placeName>; nam misit aliquot equites <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1143" cert="high">Bisontium</placeName> ac conscribit ingentem exercitum, famaque est communis et vulgaris Caesarem velle <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetios</placeName> sub iugum mittere aut turpiter ab negotio incepto infeliciter desistere.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tentabit fortunę aleam absque dubio, etsi omnes arioli extrema malo ei divinent.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Peccata nostra flagellum grave, sed paternum, speramus, iam olim pati debebant; saepe vocati ad resipiscentiam, sed frustra laborarunt pii prophetę, qui etiam sanguine suo testati sunt nos toto cęlo certare deumque iram suam effusurum contra impęnitentes.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Noster senatus arma civium futura hebdomada inspicere instituit propter novos cives, quorum magnus est numerus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchthon</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l558" cert="high">Witebergę</placeName> iterum praelegit tristi animo colligens scholam dispersam; multi ex doctis <persName ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauritio</persName> inservire nolunt atque operam suam locare in erigenda schola recusant.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdenburgum</placeName> in excommunicatione Caesaris est et parat se ad resistendum; ducem habet <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p17854" cert="high">baronem de Aldenburg</persName>, qui exutus omnibus paternis bonis exulat propter evangelium.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauricius dux</persName>, ne quid durius dicam, parat exercitum contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Madenburgenses</placeName>, cui adiunget se <placeName ref="l1041" cert="high">Brunsvicensis</placeName> incendiarius, dignum patellum ollę.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Duces <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonię</placeName>, capti ducis filii, in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l537" cert="high">Winmarckt</placeName> habitant cum matre; ditio est non procul ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l142" cert="high">Ertfordia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxoniam</placeName>, natale solum, coacti reliquere sicque expectant anxio corde patris liberationem, de qua certi nihil audimus.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concilium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinum</placeName> evangelii sparsum semen oknino suffocabit, si domini potentia non restiterit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi plura et certiora.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l28" cert="high">Basilę</placeName> 1548. 25. ianuarii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName>  D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> vocatus a Caesare ad novum colloquium in religione; veniet etiam <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchthon</persName> cum <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentio</persName>.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Videbimus mira.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> abiit die Martis 24. ianuarii.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogo etiam te, ut articulum hunc de leprosis detinendis [eher dirimendis], quem in consistorio matrimoniali observatis, ad me descriptam mittas [mittam].</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid actum obsecro in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l487" cert="high">Steckboren</placeName> cum adolescentibus?</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęec erunt initia belli <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetici</placeName> absque dubio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An meyster <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heynrich Bullinger</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>, mynem lieben gunner.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
